author: jvanzyl
msg: This element is the location on <siteAddress>, in our case jakarta.apache.org,
where we want to place our site documentation.
The maven:deploy-site produces all the documentation and then packs it
up, secure copies it to the <siteAddress> and then unpacks it in
<siteDirectory>. The <siteDirectory> entry must have a trailing slash.
